comment: /**  * The number of all rows in this column including both nulls and non-nulls.  */
code: /**  * The number of all rows in this column including both nulls and non-nulls.  */ public long getTotalCount() {     return getNullCount() + getNonNullCount(). }

comment: /**  * The number of non-null values in this column.  */
code: /**  * The number of non-null values in this column.  */ public abstract long getNonNullCount().

comment: /**  * The number of null values in this column.  */
code: /**  * The number of null values in this column.  */ public abstract long getNullCount().

comment: /**  * True if this column contains any null values.  */
code: /**  * True if this column contains any null values.  */ public boolean containsNull() {     return getNullCount() > 0L. }

comment: /**  * True if this column contains any non-null values.  */
code: /**  * True if this column contains any non-null values.  */ public boolean containsNonNull() {     return getNonNullCount() > 0L. }
